replies.body: I'm seeing quite a few of these EUNE ping spikes tonight, but so far it seems more related to a possible ISP issue. I don't wanna jump the gun and place blame of course, so let's do a little test to see what's happening. Use a tool like [WinMTR](http://winmtr.net/winmtr-v0-92-now-available/) to run a test to the EUNE servers at 31.186.224.42 and paste what you get back here so I can take a look.

IT'S NOT ONLY YOU. I HAVE THE SAME ISSUE RIGHT NOW. 7K MS.
EDIT: ONE GUY FROM ENEMY TEAM HAD THE SAME.
